question: Show me all reports and photographers with a deadline of 2021-03-18 16:30:00.
sql_query1:
SELECT reporters.Name 
FROM reporters
WHERE (reporters.role = "Reporter" OR reporters.role = "Photographer") AND reporters.deadline = "2021-03-18 16:30:00"
sql_query2:
SELECT reporters.Name 
FROM reporters
WHERE reporters.role = "Reporter" OR reporters.role = "Photographer" AND reporters.deadline = "2021-03-18 16:30:00"
interpretation1: Give me both reports and photographers where either has a 2021-03-18 16:30:00 deadline.
interpretation2: Show all the reports, then also show the photographers working to a 2021-03-18 16:30:00 deadline.
